@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - Alternative Two

autonumber

actor "HRM" as Manager
participant ":System" as System

activate Manager

    Manager -> System : asks to register a new collaborator
    activate System

        System --> Manager : shows job category list and asks to select one
    deactivate System

    Manager -> System : selects a job category
    activate System

     System --> Manager : shows docType list and asks to select one
        deactivate System

        Manager -> System : selects a docType
        activate System

        System --> Manager : requests data (i.e. name, date of birthday, admission data,\n address, email, phone number,docType,(taxpayer number/\ncitizen card number/passport number),...)
    deactivate System

    Manager -> System : types requested data
    activate System

        System --> Manager :shows all data and requests confirmation
    deactivate System

    Manager -> System : confirms data
    activate System

        System --> Manager : displays operation success / show list of existing collaborators
    deactivate System
@enduml